            "title": "A股偏軟成交縮   滬股轉升近全日高位收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股上午偏軟，兩市合計成交10771.94億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日升4點或0.15%，報3267點，今早以3260點開市，跌2點或0.07%，約10:00AM低見3246，跌16點或0.49%，為全日低位，午後市況好轉，臨近收市高見3268，升6點或0.18%。全日成交4563.33億元</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日報9858點，跌26點或0.27%，今早開市報9886點，升1點或0.02%，隨即見9895點，升11點或0.11%，為全日高位，其後向下，午後早段見9804，跌80點或0.81%，為全日低位。全日成交6208.61億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日報3761點，升2點或0.06%，今早開跌2點或0.07%，開報3756點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌2點或0.13%，報1930點，今早開市報1933點，升不足1點或0.05%。</p>\n</div>",
